      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CATCH MY SHADOW (5) was in the money last time at Casino (17.26) in a Grade 4, finishing a 3 length third. Has already won two times from this draw. Looks suited and should go close. SILENT MINUTE (7) has been a little hard to follow, finishing out of the placings latest but was in winning form two back scoring in a Grade 4/5 at Gosford. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from on outside draw. Can find the frame this time. KINGSBRAE REX (1) was safely held last time out, finishing sixth at this track over 450m behind Blow Bayou (25.92) in a Grade 5. Was in the money the start prior. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. Should be in this for a long way. MARCO MARCO (4) warrants respect with the drop in journey.",
